727 #define ADC_SR_JEOC ((uint32_t)0x00000004)
728 #define ADC_SR_JSTRT ((uint32_t)0x00000008)
729 #define ADC_SR_STRT ((uint32_t)0x00000010)
730 #define ADC_SR_OVR ((uint32_t)0x00000020)
731 #define ADC_SR_ADONS ((uint32_t)0x00000040)
732 #define ADC_SR_RCNR ((uint32_t)0x00000100)
733 #define ADC_SR_JCNR ((uint32_t)0x00000200)

745 #define ADC_CR1_JEOCIE ((uint32_t)0x00000080)

747 #define ADC_CR1_AWDSGL ((uint32_t)0x00000200)
748 #define ADC_CR1_JAUTO ((uint32_t)0x00000400)
749 #define ADC_CR1_DISCEN ((uint32_t)0x00000800)
750 #define ADC_CR1_JDISCEN ((uint32_t)0x00001000)
